data.description: Welcome to 9414 Palomino Path, a meticulously cared for home in the heart of the coveted Wildhorse Subdivision. This open concept abode features soaring ceilings, chef's kitchen, split-level double master, a dedicated office, and spacious outdoor living. The grand entry invites you in to a masterfully designed space that includes both casual and formal dining rooms. The kitchen offers ample storage and creates a superb congregation and entertaining area. Master bedrooms are located on both the first and second floor. The upstairs includes a massive second living space and the remaining bedrooms. The backyard oasis efficiently utilizes the area, geared for outdoor entertainment. All major mechanicals in the home have been replaced in the last four years to include Roof, HVAC Unit, and Water Heater to ensure worry-free comfort for years to come. Come take a look today!
